--------------------
Steps 
--------------------

1. Develop the entity class
	1. User- which Implements UserDetails
	2. Roles
	3. ManyToMany Relation 
	
2. Create a User service which implements UserDetailsService and Override loadUserByUsername()

3. Create the security configuration
	1. FilterChain bean
	2. Authentication provider
	3. PasswordEncoder
	4. AuthenticationEntryPoint for exception Handling
	5. Token Filter which implements OncePerRequestFilter
	6. LogoutHandler class which implements LogoutHadler(I)
	